      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 21,
      "message": "This was just my proposal of solving the problem of having same definition of docker container for dns image in two places (this file and in handlers). Putting docker_container only here would require removing handlers in above two tasks, while leaving the handler and task for starting container here will revert the original issue.",
